window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The first book in the scorching new Hot Jocks series by </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Kendall Ryan - available in audio first! </b> </p> <p>I've never been so stupid in my entire life. </p> <p>Elise Parrish, my teammate's incredibly sweet and gorgeous younger sister, should have been off-limits, but my hockey stick didn't get the memo. </p> <p>After our team won the championship, our flirting turned physical, and I took her to bed. Then shame sent her running the next morning from our catastrophic mistake. </p> <p>She thinks I don't remember that night - but every detail is burned into my brain so deeply, I’ll never forget. The feel of her in my arms, the soft whimpers of pleasure I coaxed from her perfect lips....</p> <p>And now I’ve spent three months trying to get her out of my head, but I’m starting to understand she’s the only girl I’ll ever want. </p> <p>I have one shot to show her I can be exactly what she needs, but Elise won’t be easily convinced. </p> <p>That’s okay, because I’m good under pressure, and this time, I’m playing for keeps. </p>"; 
